Today we were looking for vegan food in town- we found this place,  Although I am vegan, my friends  are not they had soups, and dinner specials "Wow they were  extremely happy to find this place cause we all were eating out at all the days, I had vegan soup and vegan falafel sandwich with Super mushroom coffee wow.... This is  the best I had .. we could not believe Bayonne  has this restaurant  this should be in NY,, Price is worth . Food is fresh .... You weren't be regret.. comfortable seating with air condition. Tanks to the chef your food is the best  of the best!!! We will be back again !!!
